            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台半(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5425:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5425\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5425-TW</a>)20日13:24上漲5.3元，股價漲停報58.5元，委買16,000張、委賣805,000張，成交10,391張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為整流器之生產製造．銷售及進出口業務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台半(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5425:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5425\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5425-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲1.14%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌4.68%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+135 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+191 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-3 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-53 張</li> <li>融資增減：+908 張</li> <li>融券增減：+47 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
